íŸ@183afcf7fe2e12aaa2356679e99532b33fd1075f94b5b5d54a2f1b08352371a7⁄Title: title: into bool
Path: Examples
Content:
Convert value to boolean in table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[value]; ['false'] ['1'] [0] [1.0] [true]] | into bool value
‚ï≠‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¨‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïÆ
‚îÇ # ‚îÇ value ‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îº‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î§
‚îÇ 0 ‚îÇ false ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 1 ‚îÇ true  ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 2 ‚îÇ false ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 3 ‚îÇ true  ‚îÇ
‚îÇ 4 ‚îÇ true  ‚îÇ
‚ï∞‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î¥‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚ïØ


```
Convert bool to boolean.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> true | into bool
true

```
convert int to boolean.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | into bool
true

```
convert float to boolean.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0.3 | into bool
true

```
convert float string to boolean.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '0.0' | into bool
false

```
convert string to boolean.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'true' | into bool
true

```
interpret a null as false.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> null | into bool --relaxed
false

```
interpret any non-false, non-zero string as true.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'something' | into bool --relaxed
true

```
